description:
this is the live match that was shot june 19th. It was scheduled to be the light weight championship between Darling and Savanna Fox but Darling was out with an illness so Ariel X stepped in last minute to challenge the Rookie cup champion. One wrestler dominates the other and makes her look pathetic.
These two girls recently did an Everything Butt shoot. To check it out click here
title: two hard body champions fight for the ultimate form of control
